http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: The Mathematics Standards describe what students should know and be able to do at grade levels. They reflect the increasing complexity and sophistication that students are expected to achieve as they progress through school.
Numbers, Number Systems, and Number Relationships
Count and Compare Numbers

Use models to represent the concept of equivalent forms of a fraction, decimal, and/or percent.
